data.text:
Availability: In Stock

Size: 14.75" x 20.75" (37.5 cm x 53 cm)

This product displays your Surname History in our new frame which will surely amaze you every time you pass by it.

The solid wood frame is our most luxurious frame yet. With shades of rich brown and gold, this frame is breathtaking encompassing your Surname History.

The frame is 2" thick featuring an ornate golden design with brown hues around it. Despite the embellishment of this frame it's still fairly lightweight and includes hooks on the back for hanging. The Surname History is protected by acrylic to eliminate the risk of shattering during shipment.
